{"tid":221445,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"( 新手出機一問) 單反Full Frame嘅選擇","createTime":"2017-04-28T16:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T09:41:08.000Z","uid":17032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb47e2d4894aa6ad490e5c48d6e7831df9b2049","tid":221445,"uid":17032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"話說小弟以前都淨係用屋企人部 100D玩過. 嚟緊準備去旅行想買屬於自己第一部<br />\n<br />\n嘅相機, 之後可能都會跟埋朋友出街影下景<br />\n<br />\n爬左幾日教學之後, 決定左想買部數碼單反Full Frame , 我又唔太話驚重又鍾意單<br />\n<br />\n反多過無反個觀景器<br />\n<br />\n目前睇中左 Nikon D750 ,想連埋KIT出 , 因為暫時唔知自己嘅要求想玩大路少少<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家意見 有冇更好推介 buget:~16000-18000"},{"pid":"b3a0a5c9c75cdb10318d6798b828ffce6752e9b8","tid":221445,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔考慮下5D3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3464f219b9619d515436f95d2fa62c8f5fbab45","tid":221445,"uid":17032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔考慮下5D3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驟眼睇過 好似貴啲之餘又早出少少 都可以考慮下嘅"},{"pid":"331c3989f61de8ca9a389c69ff6d7aa2519e012e","tid":221445,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"A7II + 16-35 F4<br />\n旅行夠用"},{"pid":"0d366dcd7f3dbe5f76d60b459b65633e688600d4","tid":221445,"uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"5D mark 1 平+實用"},{"pid":"223a8c4092bcf1e994ad2e2fb2e38c21ba8604ac","tid":221445,"uid":17032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A7II + 16-35 F4<br />\n旅行夠用</blockquote><br />\na7ii 真係幾正, 但始終想買部單反玩下傳統嘢先"},{"pid":"f7b46f1fd6006e3f51fd775ea0788a57740bb9b9","tid":221445,"uid":17032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5D mark 1